  "response": "In San Jose, California, there are several reputable solar panel installation providers you can consider. Some of these include:\n\n1. **SunPower** - Known for high-efficiency solar panels and comprehensive installation services.\n\n2. **Solar Technologies** - Offers residential and commercial solar solutions with a focus on customer satisfaction.\n\n3. **PetersenDean Roofing & Solar** - Provides roofing and solar installation services, ensuring compatibility between the two.\n\n4. **Clean Solar** - A local company known for personalized service and strong community involvement.\n\n5. **Tesla Energy** - Offers solar panels and the Tesla Powerwall battery for energy storage.\n\n6. **Semper Solaris** - A veteran-owned company that offers solar installation and roofing services.\n\nIt's important to compare quotes, check reviews, and consider the specific needs of your property when choosing a provider. Additionally, ensure that the installer is licensed and has experience with installations in San Jose.",
